Help:Node.title: Command Usage: !office
Help:Node.Log:Description:
COMMAND USAGE: !office
EXAMPLE: !office
Teleports you to the Skotos office. This is the place you generally will hang out when acting as a StoryGuide, and almost always the place you want to be if you're !grabbing players to talk to them.
SEE ALSO: !grab, !join, !ungrab
